main.name: Hoch-Shanahan Dining Commons
main.description:
The Dining Commons, offering more than 28,000 square feet, features open exhibition kitchen areas, seating for nearly 500, a state-of-the art pizza oven and a rotisserie oven for juicy, tender meats.

The Dining Hall Hours of Operation will vary based on College Observed Holidays, Summer Conferences, Staff Training and Other Student Programs held on Campus.

To access our Sign In Sheets for the academic year please click on the following links:

[Group Sign In Sheet](internalLink:/web/en-us/media/Group%20Sign-In%20Sheets_%202025-2026_tcm17-72877.pdf "Locations Group Sign In Sheet 25-26")

[Individual Sign In Sheet](internalLink:/web/en-us/media/Individual%20Sign-In%20Sheet_2025-2026_tcm17-72878.pdf "Locations Sign In Sheet Individual 25-26")

Check out our TASTY Video featuring our Executive Chef, Ruben Vega, making [Butterfinger Cinnamon Toast Bars](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iR9XvoNnToU&feature=youtu.be&list=PLee4zWyLfi9sw3hyh_czGukOZCBI0QSs- "Tasty Video")

main.name: Hoch-Shanahan Dining Commons
main.description:
The Dining Commons, offering more than 28,000 square feet, features open exhibition kitchen areas, seating for nearly 500, a state-of-the art pizza oven and a rotisserie oven for juicy, tender meats.

The Dining Hall Hours of Operation will vary based on College Observed Holidays, Summer Conferences, Staff Training and Other Student Programs held on Campus.

To access our Sign In Sheets for the academic year please click on the following links:

[Group Sign In Sheet](internalLink:/web/en-us/media/Group%20Sign-In%20Sheets_%202025-2026_tcm17-72877.pdf "Locations Group Sign In Sheet 25-26")

[Individual Sign In Sheet](internalLink:/web/en-us/media/Individual%20Sign-In%20Sheet_2025-2026_tcm17-72878.pdf "Locations Sign In Sheet Individual 25-26")

Check out our TASTY Video featuring our Executive Chef, Ruben Vega, making [Butterfinger Cinnamon Toast Bars](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iR9XvoNnToU&feature=youtu.be&list=PLee4zWyLfi9sw3hyh_czGukOZCBI0QSs- "Tasty Video")

main.description:
The Dining Commons, offering more than 28,000 square feet, features open exhibition kitchen areas, seating for nearly 500, a state-of-the art pizza oven and a rotisserie oven for juicy, tender meats.

The Dining Hall Hours of Operation will vary based on College Observed Holidays, Summer Conferences, Staff Training and Other Student Programs held on Campus.

main.name: Hoch-Shanahan Dining Commons
main.description:
The Dining Commons, offering more than 28,000 square feet, features open exhibition kitchen areas, seating for nearly 500, a state-of-the art pizza oven and a rotisserie oven for juicy, tender meats.

The Dining Hall Hours of Operation will vary based on College Observed Holidays, Summer Conferences, Staff Training and Other Student Programs held on Campus.

main.name: Hoch-Shanahan Dining Commons
main.description:
The Dining Commons, offering more than 28,000 square feet, features open exhibition kitchen areas, seating for nearly 500, a state-of-the art pizza oven and a rotisserie oven for juicy, tender meats.

The Dining Hall Hours of Operation will vary based on College Observed Holidays, Summer Conferences, Staff Training and Other Student Programs held on Campus.
